  <title>1.1.1 Flow Switch</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">流量开关</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">流量开关可监控机床运行期间供油的流速。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:210px; height:30px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">设置（最少流量）</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:288px; height:30px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">10 升/分钟</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:210px; height:30px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">检测信号</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:288px; height:30px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:4px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">LS170 （正常状态下 &quot;关闭 = 1&quot;）</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="page-break-before:always;"></para>
